No. 10-512. In re Grand Jury Proceedings. 562 U.S. 1054, 131 S. Ct. 616,

178 L. Ed. 2d 453,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 8992. November 15, 2010.

Motion of petitioners to unseal the petition for writ of cer-tiorari denied. Petition for writ of certio-rari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit denied.
